<dd>Fully digital, automated mixing desk<P>

<dt>Recorders:<dd>Digital 8-tk deck w/ lockup
<dd>Beta SP reference deck w/ Sonic machine control
<dd>Analog 2-tk w/ center stripe time code and lockup
<dd>DAT recorder/player
<dd>Layback to Digital Beta, 1" (Dolby&reg;, Telcom&reg;, or no noise reduction) and Beta SP<P>

<dt>Support:<dd>Wide selection of microphones
<dd>Tube pre-amps/compressors
<dd>Multiple digital effects
<dd>Midi sequencing w/ digital sampler and time code lockup
<dd>(Two) comprehensive SFX libraries
<dd>CD player<P>

<dt>Full studio with audio/video monitoring


</DL>
