<IMG SRC="stills/apple.gif" width=108 height=128 ALIGN=RIGHT alt="Apple">

<p><b>VIDEOS $24.95 ea</b>

<BR>In our 14th season: join our multi-cultural team of scientific explorers in Africa, Tahiti, the Andes and the Rainforest as well as learning about the wetlands, coyotes and earthquakes of the U.S. </p>

<p><b>SCIENCE KITS $18.00 ea</b>
<BR>Eight kits include a booklet of hands-on experiments and everything you need to carry out those experiments. </p>
<p><b>CD-ROMS Vols. 1, 2 and 3 $39.95 ea</b>
<BR>Interactive science discovery programs that explore for example: the heart, bees, roller coasters and sound. </p>
<p><b>SCIENCE CHARTS $10.00 ea</b>
<BR>Ten inquiry-based science charts include, in part, info on: tears, fire and what makes an airplane fly. </p>

	<hr>


