<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Africa Express: Hired Help - factfile</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#000000" TEXT="#FFFFFF" LINK="#00FFFF" VLINK="#FFFF00"ALINK="#FF00FF"><TABLE><TR><TD><A HREF="/index.html"><IMG SRC="/_gifs/4wobcircle.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></A></TD><TD><IMG SRC="/_gifs/wobcircle1.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></TD><TD><IMG SRC="/_gifs/wobcircle1.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></TD><TD><IMG SRC="/_gifs/wobcircle1.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></TD></TR></TABLE><BASEFONT SIZE=4><A NAME="TOP"><DL><DD><DL><DD><P><P><FONT SIZE=6>Hired Help - factfile</FONT></BODY></HTML><P><FONT SIZE=4><UL><P>	<P><LI>Executive Outcomes pays its 'advisers' $2,000-5,000 a month plusbenefits - an attractive 	proposition for former members of the South African special forces, many ofwhom are 	unemployed <P>	<P><LI>The Angolan government paid Executive Outcomes a total of 85 millionto help tip the military 	balance against the rebel forces of UNITA<P>	<P><LI>South Africa has a policy of non-intervention in the region, but theactivities of Executive 	Outcomes aren't illegal as the law stands. However, there are now moves tomake them illegal<P>	<P><LI>Since beginning his career in Katanga in 1960, Bob Denard, who has thedubious distinction of 	being Africa's most famous mercenary, has fought in Biafra, worked covertlyfor South Africa, 	and tried to destabilise the governments of Benin, Gabon and Libya<P>	<P><LI>In October 1995 Denard surrendered to French commandos after anabortive coup on the island of 	Grande Comore, in the Indian Ocean . This was the third coup Denard hadlaunched in the Comoro 	Islands<P>	<P><LI>The last mercenary venture of one of Denard's former colleagues, 'MadMike'Hoare, ended still more 	ignominiously. Attempting to enter the Seychelles by stealth, Hoare and hisassociates posed as 	a drinking club called the Loyal Order of the Froth Blowers. They never madeit out of the 	airport</UL></B></FONT><P><A HREF="#TOP"><IMG SRC="../../../_gifs/_line1.gif" WIDTH=448 HEIGHT=8BORDER=0></A><TR>			<P><TD VALIGN TOP WIDTH=88><A HREF="xphirt2.html"><IMGSRC="../xpback.gif" ALT="Background" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=88 HEIGHT=50BORDER=0></A></TD>		<P><TD VALIGN TOP WIDTH=88><A HREF="../xphome.html"><IMGSRC="../xphome.gif" ALT="Africa Express Home Page" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=88HEIGHT=50 BORDER=0></A></TD>		<TD VALIGN TOP WIDTH=88><A HREF="../xplinks/xplinks.html"><IMGSRC="../xplink.gif" ALT="Africa Links" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=88 HEIGHT=50BORDER=0></A></TD>		<TD VALIGN TOP WIDTH=88><A HREF="../xpconn.html"><IMG SRC="../xpconn.gif"ALT="Express Connections" ALIGN=TOP WIDTH=88 HEIGHT=50 BORDER=0></A></TD>		</TR></DL></DD></DL></DD></BODY></HTML>
