<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>FIRST SEX</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#000000" TEXT="#FFFFFF" LINK="#00FFFF" VLINK="#FFFF00" ALINK="#FF00FF"><TABLE><TR><TD><A HREF="/index.html"><IMG SRC="/_gifs/4wobcircle.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></A></TD><TD><IMG SRC="/_gifs/wobcircle1.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></TD><TD><IMG SRC="/_gifs/wobcircle1.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></TD><TD><IMG SRC="/_gifs/wobcircle1.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></TD></TR></TABLE><P><P><DL><DD><DL><DD><H1>FIRST SEX '95</H1><EM>First Sex</EM> is the only peaktime series on British television presenting stories from a feminist perspective. Going behind the headlines to take a perceptive look at issues with a particular significance for women, the series unearths domestic and international stories not covered elsewhere. The <A HREF="fsprog.html" NAME="">programme schedule</A> also includes updates on women's issues, and witty and imaginative short films directed by gifted newcomers. <P>Over the weeks these pages will focus on some of the key topics raised in the series, providing comment and further information, including details of useful organisations and links to other Internet sites and resources. <P><A HREF="fsnet1.html" NAME="">Women Surf the Internet:</A> what the Internet can do for women<P><A HREF="fstour1.html" NAME="">Ethical Tourism:</A> should women boycott countries with poor records on human (and particularly women's) rights?<P><A HREF="fsrap1.html" NAME="">Rape on Trial:</A> the facts and figures that spell out the need for judicial reform<P><A HREF="fspris1.html" NAME="">Prisoners' Partners</A>: the stark reality and lack of support for women whose partners are 'inside'<P><A HREF="fsblood1.html" NAME="">Blood Rites and Wrongs:</A> everything you need to know about 'the curse'<P><A HREF="fsdm1.html" NAME="">Dear Mum</A></A>: women say what they've never been able to say to their mothers<P><A HREF="fsmad1.html" NAME="">Are Women Mad to Have Children?</A>: facts, figures, frank talk and further information<P><H2>NEW</H2><EM><A HREF="fslif1.html" NAME="">It's my life</A></EM>: women with learning difficulties speak about their sexuality and their relationships<P><P><IMG SRC="../../_gifs/_line1.gif" WIDTH=448 HEIGHT=8 BORDER=0"></DL></DD></DL></DD></BODY></HTML>
