<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Pot Night</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#000000" TEXT="#FFFFFF" LINK="#00FFFF" VLINK="#FFFF00" ALINK="#FF00FF"><TABLE><TR><TD><A HREF="/index.html"><IMG SRC="/_gifs/4wobcircle.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></A></TD><TD><IMG SRC="/_gifs/wobcircle1.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></TD><TD><IMG SRC="/_gifs/wobcircle1.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></TD><TD><IMG SRC="/_gifs/wobcircle1.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></TD></TR></TABLE><P><P><DL><DD><DL><DD><H1><IMG SRC="potlogo.gif" ALT="Pot Night" ALIGN=top WIDTH=378 HEIGHT=315></H1><P>On Saturday 4 March Channel 4 devoted a whole night's programming to the subject of cannabis, plus a debate on the issue of legalising cannabis shown on Sunday 5 March.<p>These pages contain material adapted and abridged from the Channel 4 booklet published to accompany the programmes.<p>A <a href="http:potchron.html">cannabis chronology</a> charts important dates and events. <p>There are articles on the <a href="http:potplant.html">plant and its cultivation</a>, and on the <a href="http:potsci.html">science of cannabis and cannabinoids</a>, which include THC, largely responsible for the characteristic pharmacological properties of cannabis. The wider uses of cannabis, or <a href="http:pothemp.html">hemp</a>, are also covered.<p>A series of articles examine cannabis in relation to the law: <a href="http:potlaw.html">British law</a> as it stands; contrasting policy in <a href="http:potcountries.html">Sweden and The Netherlands</a>; and arguments <a href="http:propot.html">for</a> and <a href="http:antipot.html">against</a> legalisation.<p>There are a variety of resources including, <a href="http:potnet.html">Internet sites</a>, <a href="http:potorg.html">relevant organisations</a>, <a href="http:potread.html">further reading</a>, pot-influenced <a href="http:potfilm.html">films</a> and <a href="http:potmusic.html">music</a>, plus a chance to test your knowledge of pot's many <a href="http:potnames.html">names</a>.<p><P><IMG SRC="../../_gifs/_line1.gif" WIDTH=448 HEIGHT=8 BORDER=0"></DL></DD></DL></DD></BODY></HTML>
