0 years</TD><TD><CENTER>39</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>3 ?</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>5</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>-</CENTER></TD></TR><TR><TD>Treatment</TD><TD><CENTER>71</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>-</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>17</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>12</CENTER></TD></TR><TR><TD>Psychiatric services</TD><TD><CENTER>44</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>7</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>7</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>10</CENTER></TD></TR><TR><TD>Social worker</TD><TD><CENTER>5</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>-</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>3</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>-</CENTER></TD></TR><TR><TD>Counselling</TD><TD><CENTER>7</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>-</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>5</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>-</CENTER></TD></TR><TR><TD>General Practitioner</TD><TD><CENTER>12</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>1</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>2</CENTER></TD><TD><CENTER>2</CENTER></TD></TR></TABLE> 			  <P><A NAME="Call"><H2>Call Record Form</H2><P>Calling for: (% each gender)<P>Age when self harm commenced (if disclosed)<P>How long have they self harmed (if disclosed)<P>No receiving treatment<P>Main topic / reason for call<P><HR WIDTH=40% SIZE=1><p></body></html>
