<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>PERCEPTION</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#000000" TEXT="#FFFFFF" LINK="#00FFFF" VLINK="#FFFF00" ALINK="#FF00FF"><TABLE><TR><TD><A HREF="/index.html"><IMG SRC="/_gifs/4wobcircle.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></A></TD><TD><IMG SRC="/_gifs/wobcircle1.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></TD><TD><IMG SRC="/_gifs/wobcircle1.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></TD><TD><IMG SRC="/_gifs/wobcircle1.gif" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></TD></TR></TABLE><P><P><DL><DD><DL><DD><H2><A HREF="-mind.html">The Mind Field:</A> <A HREF="-percep.html"> Perception</A></H2><H3>Illusion</H3>A false impression or notion, a misleading image that deceives or misleads.<P><H3>Delusion</H3>A false belief that is held with great conviction.<P><H3>Hallucination</H3>The perception of something apparently real to the perceiver but which has no objective reality. A completely unfounded or mistaken impression.<P><P><IMG SRC="../../_gifs/_line1.gif" WIDTH=448 HEIGHT=8 BORDER=0"></DL></DD></DL></DD></BODY></HTML>
