n that can make me cry with a few sharp words.</EM><P><P><P><H2>Dear Mum</H2><P><EM>I want to say, I'm proud of you. That's something I've never managed to say to you because it took me a very long time to realise that you were someone to be proud of.</EM><P><P><P><H2>Dear Mum</H2><P><EM>I always knew you loved me exactly how I was, despite my disability. I never, ever got a message from you that you wished I'd been any other way, that you wished I'd been this mythical 'normal' daughter.</EM><P><P><IMG SRC="../../_gifs/_line1.gif" WIDTH=448 HEIGHT=8 BORDER=0"></DL></DD></DL></DD></BODY></HTML>
