<head>
<title>LOLU: The Left On Line University</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#EEFFFA" link="#CC0000" vlink="#000055" alink="#FF3300">
<h2 align=center><a href="about.htm"><img src="../gifs/lglolu.gif" alt="LOLU: The Left On Line University" align=bottom border=0 width=452 height=72></a></h2>
<hr>
<p align=center><a href="../index.htm"><img src="../gifs/smznet.gif" alt="ZNet | " align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=73 height=37></a> <a href="whatsnew.htm"><img src="../gifs/whatsnew.gif" alt="WHAT'S NEW | " align=middle border=0 hspace=5 width=56 height=54 valign="top"></a> <a href="../help.htm"><img src="../gifs/help.gif" alt="HELP | " align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=56 height=54></a> <a href="mailto:zsysop@zbbs.com"><img src="../gifs/feedback.gif" alt="Feedback | " align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=90 height=46></a> <a href="subscrib.htm"><img src="../gifs/subscrib.gif" alt="Subscribe" align=middle border=0 width=90 height=46></a> </p>
<hr>
<blockquote>
<p>The Left On Line University (another name for the ShareWorld Systems Ideas on Line 
University) provides three semesters per year of non-jargonistic, university level, fifteen-week 
courses in political, social, economic, historical, and activist topics. Notable faculty have 
included Noam Chomsky, Howard Zinn, Juliet Schor, Michael Albert, Holly Sklar, Robin 
Hahnel, Steven Shalom, and others.</p>
<p>Courses will begin anew in the first week of Februrary, 1997. To take courses you must join <a href="../lbbs/index.htm">Left 
On Line</a>.</p>
<dl>
<dt><a href="about.htm"><img src="../gifs/about.gif" alt="About LOLU" align=bottom border=0 width=92 height=22><img src="../gifs/blank.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=1 height=1><img src="../gifs/hlolu.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=96 height=28></a> </dt>
<dd>An overview of the LOLU's purpose and structure, how faculty are chosen, finances, etc. </dd>
<dt><a href="staff.htm"><img src="../gifs/staff.gif" alt="Staff" align=middle border=0 vspace=3 width=70 height=24></a> </dt>
<dd>An introduction to LOLU's ``deans'' and faculty. </dd>
<dt><a href="contents.htm"><img src="../gifs/contents.gif" alt="Contents" align=middle border=0 vspace=3 width=133 height=22></a> </dt>
<dd>Course catalogs, course outlines, and sample lectures. Plus a means for you to request 
additional courses. </dd>
<dt><a href="subscrib.htm"><img src="../gifs/subs.gif" alt="Subscribe" align=middle border=0 vspace=3 width=143 height=24></a> </dt>
<dd>How to take or audit LOLU classes and an outline of the associated costs and 
responsibilities. </dd>
</dl>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</body>

