<h1>South End Press</h1>
<p>Welcome to South End Press on the Web! We are a collectively run 18-year-old publishing group of over 
200 titles that nurture and inspire radical social change. Check out our new titles, download out of print 
books, read excerpts, place an order at 10% off, find out more about us, browse through our entire 
catalog. </p>
<p><i>Last updated: May 21, 1996.</i></p>
