<h1><img src="../gifs/subs-to.gif" alt="Subscribe to " align=absbottom hspace=2 width=185 height=24><a href="index.htm"><img src="../gifs/mdzmag.gif" alt=" Z Magazine" align=middle border=0 width=216 height=75></a> </h1>
<hr>
<p><a href="index.htm"><img src="../gifs/smzmag.gif" alt="Z Magazine | " align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=108 height=37> </a><a href="../index.htm"><img src="../gifs/smznet.gif" alt="ZNet | " align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=73 height=37> </a><a href="../help.htm"><img src="../gifs/help.gif" alt="HELP | " align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=56 height=54></a> <a href="mailto:sysop@lbbs.org"><img src="../gifs/feedback.gif" alt="Feedback" align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=90 height=46> </a></p>
<hr>
<h3>Terms</h3>
<blockquote>
<pre>
USA:
     one year . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . $26
         libraries and institutions  . . . . . 45
         low income  . . . . . . . . . . . . . 18
     two years . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 45
     three years  . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  60

Canada &amp; Mexico:
     one year . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  US $40

International:
     one year . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  US $50
</pre>
<p><em>Z</em> is published once a month, except July/August when we do a double issue and take a breather. </p>
</blockquote>
<h3>Subscribe by paper mail or fax:</h3>
<blockquote>
<p>Print out this order form and mail or fax it to us today. </p>
</blockquote>
<h3>Subscribe by phone</h3>
<blockquote>
<p>Call us at <strong>(508) 548-9063</strong> or <strong>(617) 251-0755 </strong>. Be ready to tell us </p>
<ul>
<li>your name and the address to which <br>
you would like the subscription mailed </li>
<li>your credit card number (Visa or Mastercard) <br>
and expiration date </li>
<li>which subscription you would like to purchase. </li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<h3>Subscribe by email or by electronic form</h3>
<blockquote>
<p>You may <strong>send us email with your credit card number, exp date, and address</strong> but be warned that we 
haven't the capability to accept secure connections as yet. </p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="mailto:sysop@lbbs.org">E-Mail you subscription order to Z</a></p>
</blockquote>
