<p><a href="index.htm"><img src="../gifs/smzmag.gif" alt="../Z Magazine | " align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=108 height=37></a> <a href="../index.htm"><img src="../gifs/smznet.gif" alt="../ZNet | " align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=73 height=37> </a><a href="../help.htm"><img src="../gifs/help.gif" alt="HELP | " align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=56 height=54></a> <a href="mailto:sysop@lbbs.org"><img src="../gifs/feedback.gif" alt="Feedback |" align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=90 height=46> </a><a href="subscrib.htm"><img src="../gifs/subscrib.gif" alt="Subscribe" align=middle border=0 width=90 height=46> </a></p>
