<H2>
<A HREF="index.htm"><IMG
SRC="../gifs/mdzmag.gif" ALT="Z Magazine" ALIGN="top" BORDER="0"></A>
<IMG SRC="../gifs/staff.gif" ALT=" Staff" ALIGN="top" HSPACE="4">
</H2> 
<HR>
<P><A><IMG
SRC="../gifs/smzmag.gif" ALT="Z Magazine | " ALIGN="middle" HSPACE="4" BORDER="0">
</A>
<A HREF="../index.htm"><IMG
SRC="../gifs/smznet.gif" ALT="ZNet | " ALIGN="middle" HSPACE="4" BORDER="0">
</A>
<A HREF="../help.htm"><IMG
SRC="../gifs/help.gif" ALT="HELP | " ALIGN="middle" HSPACE="4" BORDER="0"></A>
<A HREF="mailto:sysop@lbbs.org"><IMG
SRC="../gifs/feedback.gif" ALT="Feedback |" ALIGN="middle" HSPACE="4" BORDER="0">
</A>
<A HREF="subscrib.htm"><IMG
SRC="../gifs/subscrib.gif" ALT="Subscribe" ALIGN="middle" HSPACE="0" BORDER="0">
</A>
</P>
<HR> 
<BLOCKQUOTE>  
<P><EM>Z Magazine</EM> currently has a staff of only three people (really,
only three). The Z community of
<A HREF="contribs.htm">writers and artists</A> is, of course, much larger. 
</P>
<P>
Keeping a very small staff is necessary to compensate for modest material
assets. We divide the work among the three of us, with each responsible for some
 editorial functions as well as all other work, such as answering phones,
handling data entry, doing budgets, dealing with printers, etc. 
</P>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="lsargent.htm">Lydia Sargent</A> 
</LI>
<LI><A HREF="esargent.htm">Eric Sargent</A> 
</LI>
<LI><A HREF="albert.htm">Michael Albert</A>   
</LI> 
</UL>
<P>Thanks to
<A HREF="http://www.pitt.edu/~jbest2">Jimmer Endres</A> for giving a facelift
to this site. 
</P>   
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
