<html>

<head>
<title>LOLU: Staff</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFA" link="#CC0000" vlink="#000055" alink="#FF3300">
<h1><a href="index.htm"><img src="../gifs/hlolu.gif" alt="LOLU" align=bottom border=0 width=96 height=28></a><img src="../gifs/staff.gif" alt=" Staff" align=absbottom hspace=8 width=70 height=24> </h1>
<hr>
<p><a><img src="../gifs/smlolu.gif" alt="LOLU | " align=middle hspace=4 width=144 height=71> </a><a href="../index.htm"><img src="../gifs/smznet.gif" alt="ZNet | " align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=73 height=37> </a><a href="../help.htm"><img src="../gifs/help.gif" alt="HELP | " align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=56 height=54></a> <a href="mailto:sysop@lbbs.org"><img src="../gifs/feedback.gif" alt="Feedback" align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=90 height=46> </a></p>
<hr>
<blockquote>
<h1>LOLU Staff</h1>
<p>The Left On Line University currently has a staff of only one person, the sysop of LBBS, but in the future there will likely be 
some expansion. There are numerous faculty who teach, though not every semester, in the LOLU program. </p>
<ul>
