<p><a><img src="../gifs/smznet.gif" alt="ZNet | " align=middle hspace=4 width=73 height=37> </a><a href="mailto:sysop@lbbs.org"><img src="../gifs/feedback.gif" alt="Feedback" align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=90 height=46> </a></p>
