<li><a href="http://scholar.lib.vt.edu/reports/Servers-web.html"><b>Spinning the Web: Setting Up World Wide Web Server</b></a> </li>
</ul>
<p><a><b>Yahoo</b></a> is the name of a service that provides excellent guidance through the WWW, including useful listings, links, searh 
options, etc. etc. Connect with them if you want to do some serious browsing or researching on the World Wide Web. </p>
</blockquote>
