<HR>
<H1>Forum Messages from the Pop Culture Forum in LBBS</H1>
<HR>
<BLOCKQUOTE><P>The PopCult forum in LBBS discusses all manner of issues
related to popular culture, though discussion of movies and music is generally
confined to those forums, for convenience. Here there might be discussion of
culture and the media generally, of the role of sports, of advertising, of the
OJ trial, of the baseball trial, as in one message below, etc.</P></BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
