<H1>Forum Messages from the Participatory Economics Forum in LBBS</H1>
<HR>
<BLOCKQUOTE><P>The Race forum in LBBS discusses all manner of issues related
to race. Here there might be discussion of race and racism and the media, the
economy, or the polity, of racism in personal life, and so on. The exchange
reproduced below came from early April, as with all the other messages 
reproduced on these Web Pages.</P></BLOCKQUOTE>
