<h2><img src="../gifs/oldsmzma.gif" align=top hspace=4 width=108 height=37> <img src="../gifs/staff.gif" align=top hspace=4 width=70 height=24> </h2>
<hr>
<p><a href="index.htm"><img src="../gifs/smzmag.gif" alt="Z Magazine | " align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=108 height=37> </a><a href="../help.htm"><img src="../gifs/help.gif" alt="HELP" align=middle border=0 hspace=4 width=56 height=54></a> </p>
