<BLOCKQUOTE>
<H2>Lydia Sargent</H2> 
<P>Lydia Sargent is a founder and member of the staff of 
<A HREF="index.htm"><EM>Z</EM> Magazine</A>. She also co-founded South End
Press and the Z Media Institute, which she coordinates.</P>
<P>Lydia's political roots go back to the anti-Vietnam War movement and her
involvements have been varied since.</P>
<P>Lydia is also a playwrite, director, and actor of many socially relevant
plays, and has operated her own theatre group in Boston, and now in Woods Hole
MA.</P>
<P></P> 
</BLOCKQUOTE>
